’Ů@f91ce5bdcb1b200be6d84bdebeb3103833607e90a858aa907614eca400d33007ÚýTitle: title: decode hex
Path: Examples
Content:
Decode arbitrary binary data
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> "09FD" | decode hex
Length: 2 (0x2) bytes | null_char printable whitespace ascii_other non_ascii
00000000:   09 fd                                                _Ă—


```
Lowercase Hex is also accepted
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> "09fd" | decode hex
Length: 2 (0x2) bytes | null_char printable whitespace ascii_other non_ascii
00000000:   09 fd                                                _Ă—


```
